202486.「マジカル★カーニバルは ４対４の\n パーティバトル限定カボ。\n<br>\n:
Magical Carnival is a four-on-four party battle... You've got three minutes to collect carnival points by smashing candy together.
Magical Carnival starts with each player having zero carnival points. During the carnival, if you defeat an opponent, 30
points will be added to your carnival points. If you are defeated, you lose 20 percent of your carnival points, move to the
resurrection point, and then return to the carnival. And at the end of the time limit, the party with the highest point total wins.
And at the end of the carnival, the party with the highest point total wins. If you win, you get 20, if you tie, 15, if you lose,
only 10... If you lose, it's only 10... and if you beat your opponent, you get an extra stamp. Let's all work together for victory!
Also, as a special rule this time, you must enter the game alone. You can't enter with a party, so please be careful. The beauty of
carnivals is that you can have fun with people you don't even know. This is your chance to have some fun. And no chatting,
please. I'm sorry. It's a great way to create a sense of unity without having to speak to each other. I don't have to explain. I hope
you have a great time at the Magical Carnival, Cabo!

202487.「今回の特別ルールとして カーニバル中の\n 職業は オバケ あくま ミイラ男:
As a special rule, during this carnival, your occupation is limited to being a ghost, a bear, a mummy man, or a jack... These
professions cannot use magic... Special moves and parameter-raising effects learned through the unique skills of other professions will
not work... These professions can only use Chocolat Attack, Chocolat Cross, Candy Drop, and... Depending on the team, you can either
use the Jam Bomber or the Butter Bomber. The Chocolat Attack allows you to attack an opponent in a straight line. The Chocolat
Attack allows you to attack an opponent in a straight line, but you have to be careful about your aim. Chocolat Cross attacks
opponents in front, behind, to the left and right of you. You can't use it until it's charged up, so use it when you need to...
Candy Drop lets you attack anyone around you. It can't reach very far, so use it when you have a chance to get close to your opponent.
The Jam Bomber and Butter Bomber can drop Bakudan at your opponent's feet. If you're the one who gets dropped, you'd better run
for your life! You'll all be fighting with the same parameters and specials, so I hope you'll enjoy this different kind of battle...

202488.「マジカル★カーニバルが始まると 画面上部に\n 残り時間と パーティの合計ポイ:
At the top of the screen, you'll see how much time you have left and your party's total points. In the upper left corner of the
screen, you can see how many carnival points each player has. The icons above each player's head show how many carnival points
they have. The more conspicuous the icon, the more carnival points you have, so you can see...

202489.「フレンドや 同じチームのメンバーが\n マジカル★カーニバルに 参加すると\n:

friends can compete with each other for carnival points and try to get a high score!

247393.「スノーボールバトルが 始まると\n 画面中央の 上部に 残り時間と\n 個人の:
When a snowball battle begins, the time remaining and your personal score will be displayed at the top center of the screen. If
you hit an enemy, it will show you how many points you have earned on the spot, and it will add up to your score at the top of the
screen... Also, at the bottom of the center of the screen, you'll see the special moves you can use right now, so check that out!

247395.「フレンドや 同じチームのメンバーが\n スボバに参加すると スコアのランキング:

score ranking of your friends and team members.
